{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They were guarding us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So the guard that would bring us into this villa would occasionally fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "As he was sitting on the-- on the sofa bed, he was falling asleep and slept while we were working or cleaning.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we even had a chance occasionally to make believe that we are working on the radio, repairing the radio, or messing around near the radio.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we would occasionally hear the news from BBC in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So we had an idea that maybe the war is turning against the Germans, and we dared hoping at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Also, while I was-- while the guard would be sleeping at that time, when I jumped out of the window to the mill, I would go into the mill.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the Czechoslovak workers working in the mill were extremely friendly people, and they would give me anything I wanted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Whether I wanted oatmeal or grits or-- or some other products that they were making in that mill, they would allow me to take that stuff and take it with me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I would fill up my-- tie my pants at the bottom and-- and dump some stuff into them and also fill my toolbox.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I was able to bring it into the-- into the concentration camp and divide it out to-- to people that were in-- in need, in desperate need, being sick or something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I would divide it to different people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not a chance, really, to run anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had absolutely no idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, certainly, as a youngster, was-- school finishing for me some five years ago, I had no idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no idea where you would go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
